high_descs: turn around and head for the cupboard under the gas
pick up a glass bowl in the cupboard
turn around and head to the fridge
place the bowl to cool in the fridge and then take it out
turn around and head to the sink
place the bowl in the cupboard under the sink
anns.task_desc: place a cold glass bowl in the sink

high_descs: Turn around and locate the counter.
Open the bottom right cabinet and take out a bowl. Shut the cabinet door.
Carry the bowl and turn around, then move to the fridge on the right and face it.
Open the fridge, place the bowl inside and shut the door. Open the door, take the bowl out and shut the door again.
Take the bowl and turn to the left then the right to face the sink.
Open the cabinet below the sink and place the bowl on the left side. Shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Chill a bowl and place it in the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn around and walk up to the kitchen cabinet that is the second one over from the right of the stove.
Open the cabinet and take out the clear container that is in there.
Turn to your left, move past the stove, then head left to walk over to the refrigerator.
Chill the container on the top shelf of the fridge before taking it back out and closing the door.
Turn around, turn to your right, and walk over to the kitchen sink.
Place the container in the cabinet below the left sink basin and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Move a chilled container to a cabinet.
